welcome_message_body: "Welcome to beautiful Lake Forest Park, where the stunning natural surroundings and charming community await you. Known for its peaceful atmosphere and scenic views, we invite you to explore and immerse yourself in all that our city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal serves all commercial flights and houses various amenities for passengers.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal caters to private and charter flights, providing a comfortable and efficient experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Renton Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The North Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves Alaska Airlines and its codeshare partners.

terminals.name: South Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The South Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves all international flights, including those operated by Delta Air Lines and its partners.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.
